VALUEPAIR.VALUE: grep '$$TipoCarga=full' WKF*_[0-9][0-9][[0-9]*_[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9].INI | cut -f1 -d\: | sort | uniq | while read file; do rm $file; done
